column3: Tested ACK 9490ec3 (which should be similar to daa8da2), indeed fixes https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/7316#issuecomment-169938133.\n
In the future, please put these kind of details in the commit message itself. :/\n

Right, if you are doing the rebase anyway, additional info  like in a74fa1f06b3c3f75afd9f54d85d1243c7df279a9 is helpful. If a rebase is not necessary, a new pull should be created anyway, so the commit ends up in the release note logs.\n
